179903.name: Share of global cumulative CO2 emissions from flaring
179903.description: Cumulative production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from flaring since the first year of data availability, measured as a percentage of global cumulative production-based emissions of CO2 from flaring since the first year of data availability. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods. Each country's share of global CO2 emissions from flaring has been calculated by Our World in Data using global CO2 emissions from flaring provided in the Global Carbon Budget dataset. Global flaring emissions include all country emissions.
